---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Selected Work — Haider Ali"
  description="Selected programs and initiatives led by Haider Ali across design systems, AI, and digital transformation."
>
  <section class="border-b border-gray-200 py-16">
    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Design leadership with measurable impact</h1>
      <p>
        I partner with enterprise teams to design systems, launch AI-enabled experiences, and align operations so
        products ship faster with more confidence. Here are a few initiatives that show how strategy, craft, and
        governance come together.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-12 py-16">
    <article class="grid gap-8 border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.2fr)_minmax(0,1fr)]">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Enterprise Design Systems</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          Established a unified design system and governance framework across Aramco's digital ecosystem. Built cross-functional
          working groups, scaled components, and introduced measurable adoption metrics that reduced design-to-dev handoff friction
          by 40%.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <li>Design tokens and accessibility baked into multi-platform component libraries.</li>
          <li>Executive dashboards showcasing adoption, velocity, and user impact.</li>
          <li>Playbooks and rituals for onboarding new product teams in under four weeks.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-4 rounded-3xl border border-dashed border-[#0A84FF] bg-[#F5FAFF] p-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">What changed</p>
        <p>Teams moved from UI fragmentation to a shared workflow, accelerating releases while preserving brand and accessibility.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center self-start rounded-full bg-[#0A84FF] px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#086cd1]">Discuss design systems</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="grid gap-8 border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.2fr)_minmax(0,1fr)]">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">DXA Hub — Digital Experience Accelerator</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          Built a center of excellence that blends research, service design, and experimentation to incubate new experience patterns
          before scaling them enterprise-wide. DXA Hub provides frameworks, research ops, and sprint teams that can plug into any
          business unit.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <li>Multi-disciplinary pods running two-week discovery-to-delivery loops.</li>
          <li>Experience scorecards to align stakeholders on measurable outcomes.</li>
          <li>Shared repository of validated journeys, insights, and service blueprints.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-4 rounded-3xl border border-dashed border-[#0A84FF] bg-[#F5FAFF] p-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">What changed</p>
        <p>Strategic initiatives now launch with clarity on user needs, alignment across stakeholders, and a path to scale.
        </p>
        <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center self-start rounded-full border border-[#0A84FF] px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0A84FF] transition hover:bg-[#e6f2ff]">Read insights</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="grid gap-8 border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.2fr)_minmax(0,1fr)]">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">MyHome Intranet Reinvention</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          Led the redesign of the internal digital workplace, turning a static intranet into a personalized command center powered by
          human-centered AI. Introduced task automation, content intelligence, and service integrations that save employees hours each week.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <li>Adaptive layouts driven by role-based relevance and behavioral data.</li>
          <li>Conversational interfaces that surface knowledge, tools, and support flows.</li>
          <li>Unified analytics to monitor service completion time and satisfaction.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-4 rounded-3xl border border-dashed border-[#0A84FF] bg-[#F5FAFF] p-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">What changed</p>
        <p>Operational teams gained a living platform instead of a broadcast channel, with measurable gains in productivity and engagement.</p>
        <a href="/speaking" class="inline-flex items-center self-start rounded-full border border-[#0A84FF] px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0A84FF] transition hover:bg-[#e6f2ff]">Book a walkthrough</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="grid gap-8 border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.2fr)_minmax(0,1fr)]">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Croods Inc & UXIQ</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          Advising fast-moving product companies on experimentation, research cadences, and design leadership. Helped teams establish
          working agreements, hire foundational roles, and introduce rituals that keep discovery and delivery in sync.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <li>Mentorship programs pairing designers, PMs, and engineers for cross-learning.</li>
          <li>North-star narratives and metrics that tie backlog decisions to outcomes.</li>
          <li>Community-of-practice sessions that spread craft across product lines.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-4 rounded-3xl border border-dashed border-[#0A84FF] bg-[#F5FAFF] p-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">What changed</p>
        <p>Founders now have a repeatable operating rhythm for discovery, delivery, and growth.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center self-start rounded-full bg-[#0A84FF] px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#086cd1]">Start a project</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-gray-200 py-16">
    <div class="space-y-6 text-center text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Need a partner for your next transformation?</h2>
      <p>
        I work with teams through advisory retainers, embedded leadership, and focused workshops. Share what you're tackling—whether it's
        a new AI capability, a design system relaunch, or aligning executives around product strategy.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#0A84FF] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#086cd1]">Connect about work</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

